message.body: I knowwww!!! You remembered! Just got out of my last final...ugh. Gotta pack and wake up really early tomorrow. Are you done yet?
Of course I remember! Aww , well at least your done. I have 3 more finals left so that's not too bad . What time are you flying in ?
I'm getting in at 4pm tomorrow. Good luck on your finals! Have you had a good Hanukkah so far?
Thank you! Yes I have , I've been eating so many latkas my grandma keeps making them so I gained like A bazillions pounds lol
